issue.title: uneven sdf model updates cuase compatabilty issues, leading up to crash

content.raw:
I installed gdb, then entered the command:

roslaunch atlas_utils atlas_drc_vehicle_fire_hose.launch gzname:=gzserver_gdb

All I got after the warnings though were repeated messages of
[tcsetpgrp failed in terminal_inferior: Inappropriate ioctl for device]

gazebo doesn't even luanch now.

Did I do something wrong?
